message.body: Random question, I think there was a credit card number in one of my texts. I can't remember, but would that get weeded it or should I be calling someone?
No don't worry. They remove all numbers
Yeah. That's what I figured. Everything went fine! Gracias :)
Okay cool. How many texts did you send in?
About 5000. I'm bitter only since I delete them texts weekly. Oh well!
That's still a good amount. I'll let you know when I find out about the pay
Okay! I'm going to see if I can add in more...don't know if I can, but mine as well check ☺️
